    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate adequate agreement with experimental data across all five operating points. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
